    title: 'Data Rights and Portability',
    text: "Where personal data must be collected by entities, the Foundation promotes the individual's ability to access, edit, and delete their data regardless of what entity collects it. These rights enable the individual's user agents to move it freely from one entity to another within the Mee Data Network, as well as to download a copy of their data.",
    class: 'col-span-12',
