    title: 'Private Advertising',
    text: "The Foundation enables apps/sites whose service providers earn revenues from advertizing, to continue to do so. However, in contrast to prevailing adtech that relies on tracking individuals across the web, the Foundation fosters the development of private advertising technology which allows ad personalization based on a person's membership in cohorts with similar interests, but does not rely on tracking.",
